   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2" image="QN_Npc_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-a" mid="150" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>I heard the story from Stas. <FONT color=#a82424>The one</FONT> I've been wanting to meet for a very long time is currently at the Saint Haven Royal Castle.<BR>
And... only a handful of adventurers can meet him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-b" mid="152" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="151"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Can you tell me more about your story?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-b" image="QN_archer_nerwin_silhouette.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-c" mid="153" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>50 years ago, I accompanied Queen Narcilia to the Black Dragon Raid....<BR>Well, she was still called <FONT color=#a82424>Nerwin</FONT> at the time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-c" image="QN_Npc_Geraint.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-d" mid="154" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>The troops were thought to be a coalition of humans and elves. When a <FONT color=#a82424>dragon</FONT> appeared amongst us, we were in chaos.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-d" image="QN_Npc_Geraint.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-e" mid="155" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>The Gold Dragon... We were so surprised when we realized that our leader, <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT> turned into a dragon.<BR>
After the war, Karacule and Barnac hurled criticisms saying that he was a traitor.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-e" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-f" mid="156" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Many people died and got injured.<BR>But <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT> disappeared with <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT> without any apology or explanation.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-f" image="QN_archer_nerwin_silhouette.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-g" mid="157" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Lady Nerwin</FONT> was injured because she was <FONT color=#a82424>contaminated</FONT> by the Black Dragon's blood, and was quickly sent to <FONT color=#a82424>Anu Arendel</FONT>. After that, she never left Anu Arendel.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-g" image="QN_Npc_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-h" mid="158" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Even until the last moment she left here, Lady Nerwin wanted to know...<BR>
What <FONT color=#a82424>those two</FONT> were trying to do...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-h" image="QN_Npc_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-" mid="159" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Please, help me solve this age-old question that has been lingering in Lady Nerwin and me.<BR>Please ask <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT> what he has been doing up until this day.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-3" image="QN_Npc_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-3-" mid="162" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Please ask <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT> on my behalf.<BR>I want to know what he has been doing for the past 50 years.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Academic_Station.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-3-" mid="164" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine${sound:npc_SH_Jasmin_sp_05.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Master Archer Ithilien</FONT> asked you to ask <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint </FONT> some questions?<BR>Hmm… The raid of Black Dragon Karas sure lives long in many people's memories.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3" image="QN_Npc_Archer_Ishilien.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-a" mid="170" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>…Another <FONT color=#a82424>person from the raid 50 years ago</FONT>?<BR>Though time has passed, everyone seems to be stuck in the spectre of the incident.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-b" mid="171" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="166"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>It's the same for you too.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-c" mid="172" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>……Yes. Same for me….<BR>Maybe no one in this world is absolutely free from the past.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-c" image="QN_Npc_Velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-d" mid="173" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>After the battle 50 years ago, <FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT> disappeared with the Black Dragon Jewel.<BR>
I wandered around the continent to chase Velskud, and also had to find the <FONT color=#a82424>fragments of the Chaos Dragon</FONT> and seal them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-e" mid="175" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="174"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>How about Argenta?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-e" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-f" mid="176" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>After the Goddess' Dream was contaminated by the poison, the world has become more and more unstable. The contaminents spread all over the world and the monsters became stronger than ever before. Argenta had to use most of her energy in supporting the <FONT color=#a94407>Monolith</FONT> which was growing weaker.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-g" mid="178" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="177"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Can you take me to the Monolith?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-h" mid="179" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>As I've told you before, that's not possible. The <FONT color=#a82424>Monolith</FONT> is a medium connecting Goddess and this world.<BR>It is a scale measuring the world as well as stairs leading to the Goddess.<BR>There is no way a human can withstand that kind of power.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-i" mid="181" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="180"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>But I still need it.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-i" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-j" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-j" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You knew.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>The only people that know the location are <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>me</FONT>.... And <FONT color=#a82424>that girl</FONT> who can see the Goddess' dream.<BR>Is that why you want to take her?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-j" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-k" mid="189" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>I can feel your energy is different from other adventurers. Pure, but unstable....<BR>
I can feel it in your confused voice.<BR>Are you planning to reach the <FONT color=#a82424>Monolith</FONT> by using the Prophet girl?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-l" mid="190" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="182"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Yes, that's my mission.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-m" mid="191" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>What Argenta and I, or the Ancient Dragon hoped to protect is this <FONT color=#a82424>world's balance</FONT>.<BR>If someone comes in contact with the Monolith, it will cause a huge shift in the balance.<BR>
I will never allow that to happen.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-n" mid="192" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="183"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Are you going to kill me?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-o" mid="193" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>You are free to do whatever you want.<BR>But if you try to break the balance of this world, I will kill you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-p" mid="194" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="184"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>But I have my mission to fulfill as well.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-q" mid="195" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>......I don't want to kill you if I have the choice. All the other adventurers consider you as their friend.<BR>
If I kill you, then I'll become a <FONT color=#a82424>traitor</FONT> to them too.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Geraint looks agonized)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-r" mid="187" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="185"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Does being considered a traitor make you upset?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-s" mid="293" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="285"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>…I have nothing to say even if they call me a traitor.<BR>They were fatally wounded of something that cannot be cured during the fight, and I didn't have the power to save them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-s" image="QN_knight_velskud_silhouette.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-t" mid="294" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="286"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>Wouldn't it have been better to leave and be loathed upon, since I couldn't save them?<BR>They say, <FONT color=#a82424>hatred is also a driving force for humans</FONT>...<BR>
I remember someone telling me that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-t" image="QN_Npc_Velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-u" mid="295" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="287"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Was it Velskud?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-u" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-v" mid="296" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="288"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>Yes. 50 years ago, after Velskud ran away with the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon's Jewel</FONT> did I realize there was <FONT color=#a82424>someone else</FONT> who was after the jewel. Velskud had infiltrated the team under his order.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-v" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-w" mid="297" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="289"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Who?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-w" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-x" mid="298" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="290"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>I don't know. I can only guess....<BR>I don't want to disturb your future with an uncertainty.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-3-x" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4" mid="299" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="291"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Could the person be the target for Velskud's revenge?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4" image="QN_Npc_Archer_Ishilien.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-a" mid="301" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>...I don't have a clue why he betrayed the others.<BR>
Also, how he lived his life afterwards.<BR>A strong will sometimes become a powerful evil energy in an inexplicable way.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-b" mid="303" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="302"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>He is a good person in the future…</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-c" mid="305" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="304"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>You always claimed you were from the <FONT color=#a82424>future</FONT>. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Geraint becomes quiet for a moment)</FONT><BR>
Even if he is your friend in the future, it doesn't change the fact that he is threatening the world this day.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-d" mid="307" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="306"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>But he still is a good person.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-e" mid="309" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="308"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>….<BR>I never imagined he would be so kind to children</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-f" mid="311" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="310"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Is that something surprizing?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-g" mid="313" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="312"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>You're still a young human. I hope you live a healthy life without thinking about the Monolith or any malice.<BR>That is also why Argenta and I are trying our best to preserve the world's balance.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-4-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5" mid="320" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="314"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I'm sorry, but I still need to accomplish my mission.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-a" mid="216" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="80"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Please tell me his answers.<BR>I've been waiting for them for the past 50 years.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-b" mid="217" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="214"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Tell her what Geraint said)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-c" mid="254" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="82"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>To keep the balance in this world….<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Ithilien thinks to herself for a long time)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-d" mid="331" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="255"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>I see. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Ithilien sighs quietly)</FONT><BR>The two of them exist to protect this world, so I guessed they would have gone through many ordeals. Still….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-e" mid="332" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="323"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Still, would it have been too much to ask the dragons to understand what we feel?<BR>I'm not talking about difficult things like love or friendship.<BR>Me, Nerwin... even everyone else would have felt the same.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Ithilien looks confused)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-f" mid="333" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="324"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT> was our leader. Everyone trusted and liked him. That is why Karacule and Barnac were more furious when they found out the truth.<BR>They trusted him as their <FONT color=#a82424>comrade</FONT>, but had been <FONT color=#a82424>betrayed</FONT>… They must have felt that way...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-g" mid="334" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="325"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>But Geraint and Argenta left without saying a word.<BR>The ones left behind were tormented more by the cold betrayal than the painful contamination.<BR>They thought they were used and abandoned.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-h" mid="335" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="326"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#662500>But Geraint, he also….</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>(Tell her Geraint's story)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-i" mid="336" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="327"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>
…Geraint is really someone I can't hate.<BR>It would have been much easier if he had really betrayed us….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-5-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-6" mid="339" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="328"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>I could guess he would say that.<BR>I believe no one really hated him at the bottom of their hearts.. At least not me, and I believe it's the same for others.<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Ithilien smiles softly)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-" mid="318" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="83"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>…I talked too much.<BR>Go out to the brighter world and do your work rather than be dragged down by me and the past.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-6" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-6-" mid="230" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="102"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>…I talked too much.<BR>Go out to the brighter world and do your work rather than be dragged down by me and the past.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-6" image="QN_Npc_Geraint.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ishilien.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-6-" mid="329" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="103"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>
If he shared even the slightest part of what we felt, maybe we didn't have to feel so bad.<BR>
Anyway, thank you for bringing answers to my long-awaited questions, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.<BR>
 <BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>*Talk to Academic Station.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-6" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Jasmin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-6-a" mid="271" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="108"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine${sound:npc_SH_Jasmin_sp_01.ogg}<BR>I see. That must be what happened about 100 years ago from now. The raid of <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon Karas</FONT> surely has affected many lives.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-6-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Jasmin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-6-b" mid="272" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="110"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine$<BR>The Prophet seems still asleep. How will the <FONT color=#a82424>Gold Dragon's Nest</FONT> be deactivated?<BR>I still don't get it. There were no records that I could find… I'm a little worried.</html>]]></talk_question>
